snippet.title: Umbraclaw - Story Trailer - "A Partner's Promise"
snippet.description:
Introducing a look at Umbraclaw's story, featuring the theme song "A Partner's Promise", sung by Tsukumo (Yuko Natsuyoshi)!
Torn from peaceful days together, Kuon must venture home while Tsukumo wishes for her return... See their story in this new trailer! 

Official website http://umbraclaw.com/en/
Steam Store https://store.steampowered.com/app/2428420/Umbraclaw/
My Nintendo Store https://www.nintendo.com/us/store/products/umbraclaw-switch/
